    function: 
    ---------  It is a sub program in a main program to perform,
    a specific task.	

    To design any function, there are 3 aspects.

    1) function declaration : it is an intimation to a compiler
       --------------------  that what type of function it is.

    2) function call : To call a function. 
       ---------------	
    3) function definition : actual function implementation.
       --------------------	

	syntax for function :
	--------------------------

	return-type function_name(arguements);


