   variable :  it is a name to a memory to store a value. 
   ---------   the value can be changed during run-time.

   there are 2 types of variables.
   1) local variables
   2) global variables.

   1) local variable: the variable data should be used with in 
      --------------- the function only.

   2) global variable: the variables data can be used in  
      ---------------- anywhere in the program among all fuctions.		

